name: Caroline Podlewski
description:
Caroline Podlewski is a French artistic director and model. She lives in Paris, France. She has a vast professional experience in different sectors. Her studies and work experiences make her a true modern entrepreneur: Caroline is so attentive to her career that her professional reputation far exceeds that of a model.

If you like my work, a review is more than welcome! Also, follow me on Twitter or Instagram!

Looking for something... spicy? Here's my Patreon!

Also, I recently started a blog where I will gather resources and tutorials about my work here!

Hey everyone! This is my textual inversion of Caroline Podlewski. I used 50 images of her, with an 8700 steps process. Hope you'll like it! To use it in your works:

  • download the file and place it into stable-diffusion-webui>embeddings folder;

  • add carpodlewski to your prompt;

  • keep the sampling steps around 20, and CFG between 7 and 9 to work well. Great results with DPM++ 2M Karras & Edge of Realism. Face restore could help sometimes, especially when the image is not a close-up/portrait;
